# Build context is the repo root (tools import shared ./security). Keep the context
# small and never ship secrets or host-built venvs into an image.
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.git
.gitignore
.ruff_cache
.pytest_cache
vendor/
docs/
scripts/
fuckme.md

# Secrets & host state -- env is injected by the substrate (compose / task def), never baked.
**/.env
**/*.env
!**/env.example

# Per-tool systemd units are the OTHER (hardened-host) substrate; not needed in the image.
**/systemd/
